Just dropping a log file with no context isn't helpful. How does the game crash? What mods are you using? I see many in the logs but a mod list would be very helpful.

The logs don't indicate that there was a crash, however there are some B9 part switch exceptions relating to OPT tanks so this might be a good place to start- check your versions are up to date and if they are, remove OPT and see if it works then.
